{"tid":1103170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵本月二十二日開始  五六日增列車班次","createTime":"2019-04-12T08:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T09:53:13.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"189223083c2784249ff8cefb2918db4599345851","tid":1103170,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JsFzfhm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJsFzfhm.png&h=0fec7b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵由本月二十二日開始，於星期五、周末及公眾假期增加列車班次。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵港島綫、荃灣及觀塘綫每星期將額外增加合共八十六班車，港島綫增加最多，共三十八班，其次是觀塘綫增加三十四班，荃灣綫加 十四班車，新安排會縮減乘客候車時間，由數秒至半分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指自二零一二年開始，於重鐵網絡每星期已累計增加超過三千二百班車，輕鐵網絡每星期累計增加逾六百班車。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UxLRz5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UxLRz5&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8Mg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=ae78e1a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UxLRz5</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪變相影響平日班次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0092adac790cf4c1d339cf36a229102d6b608113","tid":1103170,"uid":207462,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:25:46.000Z","msg":"錯 因爲港鐵成日壞<br />\n為咗要確保服務準時率繼續係99.99%<br />\n所以要加車拉番條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9906c0844d0d5d2ce869f312ce0ee2ffb59d89","tid":1103170,"uid":66331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"加左咪又係次次停沙田俾班支通車過先"},{"pid":"6837f77069e7b0d376ab8db2ce647ee0d610c674","tid":1103170,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:35:38.000Z","msg":"增加班次仲易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9eafd268fec705d289e4ee80d4f7d89a36dc8b","tid":1103170,"uid":216654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋下點解星期一至四唔加"},{"pid":"2119